Gen Xer here. I left this country a long time ago because the writing was on the wall in the 90s.  To be back here for a minute and to see it just before collapse is just fucking depressing. I would not have lasted a fucking minute in this

depraved globohomo nightmare. To the young'uns: good fucking luck kids. I weep.
